OL,3,CUK to see more intense tropical-style
OL,4,Cthunderstorms later this week
OL,6,FHave we got more thunderstorms
OL,7,Fforecast?
OL,9,FFurther severe thunderstorms remain
OL,10,Flikely in the coming days as the
OL,11,Fwarmth and humidity continue to feed
OL,12,Funstable upper air conditions across
OL,13,Fthe UK.
OL,15,FWhen the atmosphere stays "charged"
OL,16,Flike this, any additional daytime
OL,17,Fheating can trigger new thunderstorms.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
