CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1782245910
OL,3,CUK to see more intense tropical-style
OL,4,Cthunderstorms later this week
OL,6,FThe exact time and location of further
OL,7,Fstorms are tricky to pinpoint. The
OL,8,Frisk typically comes during the
OL,9,Fhottest part of the day, with rising
OL,10,Fair.
OL,12,FBut also by night, too, as
OL,13,Ftemperatures last night didn't drop
OL,14,Fmuch below 18-20C in some areas.
OL,16,FThe next few days will see a prime set
OL,17,Fup for thundery conditions, with
OL,18,Fsoaring temperatures and warm and
OL,19,Fmuggy nights.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
